{
  "name": "Earth Spider Sewing",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Bukijutsu.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You lace an area with razor sharp wires less than a foot above  ground level. Trapping, damaging, and hindering all creatures who aren't aware of them or their locations exactly.</p><p>For the duration,  select a space the size of a 60-foot cube to fill with razor sharp wires. Select creatures that you can see to be unaffected by this jutsu.</p><p>For the duration, creatures who enter the radius of this jutsu move as if the area this jutsu inhabits is difficult terrain.</p><p>Creatures who cast Jutsu with a Mobility (M) component, must  succeed a Dexterity saving throw being restrained by the wires as they get wrapped up inside of them on a failed save.</p><p>Creatures who make weapon attacks must succeed a Strength saving throw, having their weapon caught on a wire and being unable to complete the attack on a failed save. </p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
